# 🧠 OMEGA ULTRA v4

> Next-generation multi-agent AI orchestration platform

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)
![Architecture](https://img.shields.io/badge/architecture-monorepo-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-lightgrey)
![AI](https://img.shields.io/badge/powered%20by-multi--agent-purple)

---

## 🚀 Overview

**OMEGA ULTRA v4** is a scalable, modular AI platform that enables collaboration between multiple intelligent agents, tools, and services.

It acts as a **central brain** that:
- decomposes tasks
- selects optimal models
- orchestrates execution
- manages memory and costs
- coordinates agents and tools

Built for:
- AI automation platforms
- autonomous agent systems
- SaaS AI products
- research & experimentation
- production-grade AI orchestration

---

## ✨ Key Features

🤖 Multi-agent system (coding, research, planning, negotiation)  
🧠 Intelligent orchestrator with task planning  
⚡ LLM routing based on complexity & cost  
💾 Persistent memory system  
📡 Event-driven architecture (event bus)  
💰 Cost control & usage tracking  
🔌 Pluggable tools & registry system  
🧩 Extensible marketplace-ready architecture  
🌐 FastAPI backend API  
📦 Monorepo structure for scalability  

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD

A[User Request] --> B[API Layer]
B --> C[Orchestrator]

C --> D[LLM Router]
C --> E[Memory]
C --> F[Event Bus]
C --> G[Cost Control]

C --> H[Agents]

H --> H1[Coding Agent]
H --> H2[Research Agent]
H --> H3[Planning Agent]

H --> I[Tools]

I --> I1[Web Tool]
I --> I2[DB Tool]
I --> I3[Code Executor]

C --> J[Marketplace]
C --> K[Billing System]
````

---

## 🧠 Core Components

### 🧭 Orchestrator

Central execution engine responsible for:

* task analysis
* planning
* execution
* result aggregation

### 🧠 LLM Router

Selects the best model based on:

* task complexity
* input size
* cost constraints

### 💾 Memory System

Stores:

* task history
* intermediate outputs
* contextual knowledge

### 📡 Event Bus

Enables asynchronous communication between components via pub/sub.

### 💰 Cost Control

Prevents overspending by:

* tracking usage
* enforcing budgets
* limiting execution

---

## 🤖 Agents

* **Coding Agent** → code generation & debugging
* **Research Agent** → information gathering
* **Planning Agent** → task decomposition
* **Negotiation Agent** → coordination between agents
* **Economic Agent** → cost & pricing reasoning
* **Hybrid Reasoning Agent** → mixed reasoning strategies

---

## 🔌 Tools

* 🌍 Web Tool → external data retrieval
* 🗄️ DB Tool → database operations
* ⚙️ Code Executor → safe code execution
* 📚 Tool Registry → dynamic tool management

---

## 📦 Project Structure

```text
omega-ultra-v4/
├── core/              # Brain of the system
├── agents/            # AI agents
├── tools/             # External integrations
├── marketplace/       # Plugins & ranking
├── billing/           # Usage & pricing
├── business_brain/    # Revenue optimization
├── sdk/               # Developer SDKs
├── api/               # Backend API
├── ui/                # Dashboard
├── infra/             # Deployment configs
├── configs/           # System configs
├── tests/             # Testing suite
└── scripts/           # Utilities
```

